\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for latest news on the Paris Olympics  The segment featured one of the stars of RuPaul's Drag Race, Nicky Doll, alongside Drag Race France pair Paloma and Piche.\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 561, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drag_Race_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Drag Race France\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drag_Race_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drag_Race_France\"}, {\"begin\": 561, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drag_Race_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Drag Race France\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drag_Race_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drag_Race_France\"}, {\"begin\": 583, \"end\": 589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 0.9995016948831803, \"rank\": 0.0004984947016580587, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The drag queens and other performers were arranged in a configuration that looked similar to that of Jesus Christ and his apostles in Leonardo da Vinci's 'The Last Supper' and received a mixed reception.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9928925755094232, \"rank\": 0.007158301373375721, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}, {\"begin\": 736, \"end\": 753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6698212674062204e-18, \"t